description: Defines a Java class 'GraphResult' used as a Data Transfer Object (DTO) for representing a graph with nodes, relationships, and optional Cypher script in a Neo4j context. Includes nested static classes 'Node' and 'Relationship' to model graph components.

classes.name: GraphResult
classes.description: Represents the output graph consisting of nodes and relationships, with an optional Cypher script.

classes.name: Node
classes.description: DTO representing a node in the graph. Ensures uniqueness by label and name externally.

classes.name: Relationship
classes.description: DTO representing a directed relationship (edge) between nodes.
